# ============================================
# Leads are stored server-side via /api/leads.php (the single source of truth).
# The admin panel reads/writes leads there so every browser/device stays in
# sync. REACT_APP_LEADS_API_URL + REACT_APP_LEADS_ADMIN_KEY (above) configure it.
# ============================================
